args.code:
from PyPDF2 import PdfReader

pdf_path = './1-DPO/direct-preference-optimization/paper.pdf'
reader = PdfReader(pdf_path)

# Extract the first 5 pages for DPO loss definition
text = ''
for i in range(min(5, len(reader.pages))):
    text += reader.pages[i].extract_text() + '\n'

print(text[:3000])
